hopobject.body: I can't hear you very well bsp pharmaceuticals spa Senior analyst Michael Inouye notes, "Despite stiff competition from a range of connected CE devices, the smart set-top box and dongle market offers an equally compelling user experience often at significantly lower price points. Google’s Chromecast device in particular sets a new low price bar for the connected CE market and as more applications are added to its library its value to price ratio will continue to grow."
